:Class IconSimple : MiPageSample
⍝ Control:: _DC.Icon
⍝ Description:: Icons from FontAwesome, Syncfusion, and Google

    ∇ Compose;p
      :Access Public
     
      ⍝ !!! NOTE !!!
      ⍝ remove the next three lines when xxIcon resources are added
      Add _.StyleSheet'http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.6.3/css/font-awesome.min.css'
      Add _.StyleSheet'https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons'
      Use'sfTheme'
      
      Add _.style '.red {color: red;}'
      
